  <item rdf:about="2026/0613-kamakura/">
            <title>2026/06/13: 鎌倉ハイキング</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0613-kamakura/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>平日が雨続きなので土曜日に鎌倉来たら、一年で一番混んでる時期だった。しまった。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1300" data-timestamp="2026-06-13 13:22:38"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1301" data-timestamp="2026-06-13 13:29:47"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1302" data-timestamp="2026-06-13 13:31:11"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>定点観測。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1303" data-timestamp="2026-06-13 16:18:44"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-06T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

