  <item rdf:about="2026/0610-interop/">
            <title>2026/06/10: Interop</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0610-interop/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>久しぶりに幕張へ。間違えて稲毛駅に行って引き返してきた。出遅れた。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1281" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 09:42:53"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1282" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 09:43:11"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1284" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 10:13:38"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>NOCエリア。製品名が分からないのはともかく、技術名がわからない。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1285" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 13:53:07"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1286" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 14:03:54"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1287" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 14:42:15"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>NASAの月面基地建設計画の話を聞く。エキサイティングだ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1289" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 17:24:20"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1290" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 17:28:07"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1291" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 17:32:26"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>ソフトルータ推進委員会の飲み会に混ぜてもらう。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://tabelog.com/chiba/A1201/A120102/12036099/">Azzurro520 海浜幕張店</a>
千葉県千葉市美浜区ひび野1-7 ROOMDECO 1F
050-5571-4613
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1292" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 19:24:35"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1293" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 19:38:31"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1294" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 19:43:30"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1295" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 20:09:28"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1296" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 20:24:26"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1297" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 20:44:59"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1298" data-timestamp="2026-06-10 20:45:02"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-06T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2026/0605-dinner/">
            <title>2026/06/05: 横浜飲み</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0605-dinner/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>アラクサラ時代の辞めてから会っていない同僚と飲み。</p>

<pre class="address">
